author: @haylow2701
text: what i really love abt svt so much is that no matter whether its the title tracks or bsides, their formation will never fail to give a spotlight for every member and for a 13 member group that's really impressive. so many other groups that ive stan and observe end up with the non dance line members becoming the back dancers. even with the line distribution, svt is not afraid to give the chorus to non vocal line members so every songs will always be refreshing and new to the ears. in the kpop scene even with fewer members this is a pretty rare feat to achieve, making svt all the more impressive despite having 13 members. props to the staff and the members for making this possible!!! <3
